Jose R. RODRIGUEZ, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
WELLS FARGO BANK, N.A., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-2791 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 01, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:
